simlfs
------------------------------------------
SimLFS aims at providing a clean API and a simple implementation
(C++ library) of an airline-related Low Fare Search (LFS) system. That
library uses the Standard Airline IT C++ object model
(https://github.com/airsim/stdair).

Runtime requirements:
  bash-5.2.21-1
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libairinv1.00-1.00.15-1bl1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libsimfqt1.00-1.00.13-1bl1
  libsimlfs-devel-1.00.8-1bl1
  libsimlfs1.00-1.00.8-1bl1
  libstdair1.00-1.00.26-1bl1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  doxygen-1.17.0-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libairinv-devel-1.00.15-1bl1
  libsimfqt-devel-1.00.13-1bl1
  libstdair-devel-1.00.26-1bl1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/airsim/simlfs

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/airsim/simlfs/archive/refs/tags/v1.00.8.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack simlfs-1.00.8-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./simlfs-1.00.8-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/simlfs-1.00.8-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/simlfs-1.00.8-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsimlfs1.00-1.00.8-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsimlfs-devel-1.00.8-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(simlfs)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/simlfs.README
  /usr/share/doc/simlfs/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/simlfs/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/simlfs/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/simlfs/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/simlfs/README.md

(libsimlfs1.00)
  /usr/bin/cygsimlfs-1.00.dll

(libsimlfs-devel)
  /usr/bin/simlfs-config
  /usr/include/simlfs/SIMLFS_Service.hpp
  /usr/include/simlfs/SIMLFS_Types.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/simlfs/simlfs-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/simlfs/simlfs-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/simlfs/simlfs-library-depends-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/simlfs/simlfs-library-depends.cmake
  /usr/lib/libsimlfs.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/simlfs.pc
  /usr/share/aclocal/simlfs.m4

